WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
♪And met your steady gaze♪

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
♪We made a promise long ago♪

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
♪For all our days to come♪

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
♪Holding you close♪

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
♪Would that be enough?♪

00:00:58.875 --> 00:01:00.179
=Echoes of Love=

00:01:00.180 --> 00:01:01.580
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.712 --> 00:01:03.645
=Episode 1=

00:01:08.025 --> 00:01:11.978
(Huanyue House)

00:01:11.979 --> 00:01:14.620
(A place every woman
in the realm longs to be.)

00:01:15.020 --> 00:01:17.700
(If a woman could rise to the very top,)

00:01:18.100 --> 00:01:19.340
(she could lift her family)

00:01:19.460 --> 00:01:21.260
(and ensure they'd never starve again.)

00:01:21.900 --> 00:01:24.220
(Blessed with boundless
wealth and splendor.)

00:01:24.859 --> 00:01:26.980
(Honored for the rest of her life.)

00:01:36.820 --> 00:01:38.858
(But when I gave it everything I had,)

00:01:38.859 --> 00:01:41.299
(and finally became the top courtesan,)

00:01:41.536 --> 00:01:42.574
(I realized)

00:01:42.575 --> 00:01:44.615
(it was a hell that would
consume me whole.)

00:01:44.940 --> 00:01:46.780
(No matter what it takes,)

00:01:46.979 --> 00:01:48.819
(I will expose their crimes.)

00:01:49.820 --> 00:01:53.060
(Huanyue House)
Commander Gu of the Imperial Guard

00:01:53.339 --> 00:01:55.698
has paid a fortune to redeem

00:01:55.699 --> 00:01:58.019
top courtesan Liu Ruyan

00:02:03.537 --> 00:02:07.695
(Gu Chengye,
Commander of the Imperial Guard)

00:02:12.420 --> 00:02:13.740
Where did that blood come from?

00:02:28.499 --> 00:02:30.300
Isn't that Liu Ruyan?

00:02:31.587 --> 00:02:33.932
(Modern Hangzhou)

00:02:34.020 --> 00:02:35.938
(For a thousand years,)

00:02:35.939 --> 00:02:39.259
(They've called Liu Ruyan
a shameless harlot.)

00:02:40.260 --> 00:02:41.740
I don't believe it

00:02:42.099 --> 00:02:44.139
You're not the woman they claim you are

00:03:21.379 --> 00:03:23.900
Huanyue House...

00:03:24.539 --> 00:03:25.859
(Huanyue House)
They all say I tarnished

00:03:25.860 --> 00:03:27.419
its name.

00:03:29.219 --> 00:03:30.539
Who's there?

00:03:32.819 --> 00:03:35.299
A courtesan's daughter. A loose woman.

00:03:35.300 --> 00:03:37.070
They say I have no virtue.

00:03:38.580 --> 00:03:40.300
(Liu Ruyan?)

00:03:44.580 --> 00:03:47.939
Haven't beautiful women
always been blamed for disaster?

00:03:48.350 --> 00:03:51.047
Did anyone ever care
what I went through?

00:03:53.687 --> 00:03:55.180
A thousand twists of fate,

00:03:56.725 --> 00:03:58.964
yet none of it is in our hands.

00:04:11.425 --> 00:04:15.695
(Impure. Immoral. Debauched.
Unfaithful. Courted by countless men.)

00:04:20.162 --> 00:04:22.007
(Faded beauty. An unchaste woman.)

00:04:28.339 --> 00:04:30.139
(Disloyal and shameless.)
(I need your help)

00:04:30.140 --> 00:04:32.059
(to uncover the truth)

00:04:32.580 --> 00:04:34.460
(and clear my name.)

00:05:04.419 --> 00:05:06.380
I can't believe
Liu Ruyan is still alive.

00:05:06.739 --> 00:05:08.099
Ruyan?

00:05:12.162 --> 00:05:13.561
(Did I become Liu Ruyan?)

00:05:14.539 --> 00:05:16.778
Liu Ruyan flirts
with men every day.

00:05:16.779 --> 00:05:18.218
She has no virtue to speak of.

00:05:18.219 --> 00:05:18.978
Maybe

00:05:18.979 --> 00:05:20.059
she miscarried.

00:05:20.179 --> 00:05:21.858
That's a grave taboo in Huanyue House.

00:05:21.859 --> 00:05:23.700
No wonder she jumped
to escape punishment.

00:05:23.900 --> 00:05:25.259
My lord, Liu Ruyan is in trouble.

00:05:25.260 --> 00:05:25.939
We...

00:05:25.940 --> 00:05:27.859
She's merely a blade.

00:05:28.380 --> 00:05:30.380
Whether she can be useful to me

00:05:31.260 --> 00:05:33.140
depends on how she handles this.

00:05:33.380 --> 00:05:35.220
All this noise

00:05:35.539 --> 00:05:36.859
is utterly disgraceful.

00:05:37.062 --> 00:05:41.220
(Zhou Zihua, Boss of Huanyue House)

00:05:43.859 --> 00:05:46.659
Liu Ruyan, as the top courtesan,

00:05:47.179 --> 00:05:49.059
you should have kept yourself pure.

00:05:49.739 --> 00:05:52.419
And yet you've done something so filthy.

00:05:52.979 --> 00:05:54.939
Huanyue House has always been

00:05:54.940 --> 00:05:56.340
a place of refinement.

00:05:56.900 --> 00:05:59.739
We value our ladies' reputations

00:05:59.775 --> 00:06:01.255
and chastity above all.

00:06:02.380 --> 00:06:03.499
Now,

00:06:04.020 --> 00:06:06.059
I cannot keep you here.

00:06:08.350 --> 00:06:09.550
Shangguan Yu.

00:06:10.940 --> 00:06:12.940
By the rules of Huanyue House,

00:06:13.262 --> 00:06:14.942
what is her punishment?

00:06:17.875 --> 00:06:19.075
By our code,

00:06:19.700 --> 00:06:21.340
for the crime of impurity,

00:06:22.900 --> 00:06:23.819
she must be caged

00:06:23.820 --> 00:06:25.099
and drowned.

00:06:25.700 --> 00:06:27.220
What?

00:06:27.539 --> 00:06:29.020
I'm not Liu Ruyan!

00:06:37.700 --> 00:06:38.859
I'm not...

00:06:42.500 --> 00:06:43.579
My name is Song Zhiyun!

00:06:43.580 --> 00:06:44.920
I'm not Liu Ruyan!

00:06:45.539 --> 00:06:47.059
You've got the wrong person!

00:06:58.219 --> 00:07:00.059
I paid to redeem her life.

00:07:02.750 --> 00:07:04.178
You dare pass judgment on her?

00:07:04.179 --> 00:07:05.619
It's unfortunate for Official Gu.

00:07:05.620 --> 00:07:07.939
He just spent a thousand taels
of gold to free her,

00:07:07.940 --> 00:07:08.858
and this happens.

00:07:08.859 --> 00:07:09.619
Exactly.

00:07:11.179 --> 00:07:12.220
Official Gu?

00:07:14.737 --> 00:07:16.418
(Gu Chengye...)

00:07:16.419 --> 00:07:18.539
(He made a deal with Liu Ruyan.)

00:07:19.260 --> 00:07:21.099
I want to make a deal with you.

00:07:24.487 --> 00:07:26.261
I'm just a helpless woman.

00:07:26.262 --> 00:07:27.302
What would I know

00:07:27.303 --> 00:07:29.395
about the schemes
of powerful men?

00:07:30.380 --> 00:07:31.619
Your freedom.

00:07:33.012 --> 00:07:34.132
Miss Liu.

00:07:34.412 --> 00:07:36.093
Help me investigate this case,

00:07:36.219 --> 00:07:38.382
and I'll buy back your freedom.

00:07:39.779 --> 00:07:41.780
(He's the only one who can save me.)

00:07:43.175 --> 00:07:44.900
I didn't miscarry.

00:07:45.020 --> 00:07:45.778
Someone pushed me

00:07:45.779 --> 00:07:47.059
over the railing.

00:07:47.060 --> 00:07:48.140
Someone tried to kill me.

00:07:48.339 --> 00:07:49.580
Who would want you dead?

00:07:59.500 --> 00:08:01.099
Looks like you don't remember.

00:08:01.500 --> 00:08:02.859
Then saving you

00:08:03.912 --> 00:08:05.161
is pointless.

00:08:11.900 --> 00:08:13.340
I remember now.

00:08:16.287 --> 00:08:17.847
I remember.

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:19.978
You said you'd marry me
after we slept together?

00:08:21.820 --> 00:08:22.499
Wait,

00:08:22.500 --> 00:08:25.418
does Liu Ruyan have a relationship
with the Commander?

00:08:25.419 --> 00:08:27.298
Is he trying to protect her?

00:08:27.299 --> 00:08:28.999
He looks so upright,

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:30.379
but he's just another lecher.

00:08:30.380 --> 00:08:31.619
Official Gu!

00:08:32.612 --> 00:08:34.420
I told you.

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:37.211
We should wait
until after we're properly wed.

00:08:37.275 --> 00:08:38.418
Official Gu,

00:08:38.419 --> 00:08:40.779
why are you always in such a hurry?

00:08:44.750 --> 00:08:45.989
Let go.

00:08:46.625 --> 00:08:47.506
No.

00:08:48.459 --> 00:08:49.340
Release me.

00:08:50.179 --> 00:08:51.340
You can't just abandon me.

00:08:52.340 --> 00:08:53.859
If you won't take responsibility,

00:08:53.860 --> 00:08:54.660
I swear

00:08:55.500 --> 00:08:57.340
I won't let this go.

00:09:06.179 --> 00:09:07.420
What are you doing?

00:09:08.419 --> 00:09:09.460
Get me out of here.

00:09:10.620 --> 00:09:11.779
Liu Ruyan,

00:09:12.179 --> 00:09:13.220
this blade

00:09:13.712 --> 00:09:15.653
shouldn't be at my throat.

00:09:22.059 --> 00:09:23.499
If you want to leave,

00:09:23.699 --> 00:09:24.820
it's simple.

00:09:25.620 --> 00:09:27.300
Tell me everything you know.

00:09:30.037 --> 00:09:31.395
Get me out of here first,

00:09:31.396 --> 00:09:32.586
then I'll tell you.

00:09:32.587 --> 00:09:34.060
You're bargaining with me?

00:09:34.625 --> 00:09:36.099
Then stay here

00:09:36.340 --> 00:09:38.259
and fend for yourself.

00:09:42.659 --> 00:09:43.619
Zhou Zihua,

00:09:44.179 --> 00:09:45.820
the redemption contract is void.

00:09:46.059 --> 00:09:48.019
Return my money.

00:09:48.539 --> 00:09:49.700
We're even.

00:09:50.220 --> 00:09:52.300
Huanyue House has its rules.

00:09:53.059 --> 00:09:55.019
Once the money's paid,

00:09:55.220 --> 00:09:56.499
it's nonrefundable.

00:10:01.939 --> 00:10:03.180
In that case,

00:10:03.562 --> 00:10:05.895
she'll stay and work off her debt.

00:10:07.419 --> 00:10:09.107
But remember this, Zhou Zihua.

00:10:09.860 --> 00:10:11.499
As long as she owes me money,

00:10:11.860 --> 00:10:12.859
her life

00:10:13.220 --> 00:10:14.540
belongs to me.

00:10:19.740 --> 00:10:21.619
If she can't be a courtesan anymore,

00:10:21.659 --> 00:10:23.899
then she'll serve as a lowly maid.

00:10:23.980 --> 00:10:25.298
From this day forward,

00:10:25.299 --> 00:10:27.538
there is no more
Top Courtesan Liu Ruyan.

00:10:27.539 --> 00:10:29.340
Yes, Master Zhou.

00:10:29.659 --> 00:10:32.139
I'll make sure

00:10:32.140 --> 00:10:33.859
she's properly disciplined.

00:10:41.562 --> 00:10:43.642
Did you hear Master Zhou?

00:10:43.900 --> 00:10:44.899
From now on,

00:10:44.900 --> 00:10:47.298
you're the lowest servant
in Huanyue House.

00:10:47.299 --> 00:10:49.300
Stay here and pay off your debt.

00:10:53.250 --> 00:10:55.720
(Three days later)

00:11:01.059 --> 00:11:04.060
(I heard Official Gu came back
to Huanyue House today.)

00:11:04.220 --> 00:11:06.220
(If I want to make it
out of here alive,)

00:11:06.419 --> 00:11:07.658
(I need to find out)

00:11:07.659 --> 00:11:09.460
(what he wants Liu Ruyan
to investigate.)

00:11:21.225 --> 00:11:21.864
My lord,

00:11:21.865 --> 00:11:23.505
they're watching Miss Song.

00:11:26.699 --> 00:11:28.979
So the fish finally bit.

00:11:44.299 --> 00:11:46.660
(What does he mean, the fish bit?)

00:11:49.059 --> 00:11:50.578
I told you to work!

00:11:50.579 --> 00:11:52.460
And you're slacking off here?

00:11:53.380 --> 00:11:54.499
Madam Du,

00:11:54.860 --> 00:11:56.139
you've misunderstood.

00:11:56.340 --> 00:11:58.660
(Su Wanniang, Performer)
Miss Song isn't being lazy.

00:11:58.740 --> 00:12:01.139
She's helping me
with my hair and makeup.

00:12:04.299 --> 00:12:05.660
Come. With me.

00:12:20.340 --> 00:12:22.660
May I ask, who are you?

00:12:23.059 --> 00:12:24.058
Sister,

00:12:24.059 --> 00:12:25.619
have you really lost your memory?

00:12:26.140 --> 00:12:27.580
I'm Wanniang.

00:12:28.819 --> 00:12:30.818
Why are you helping me?

00:12:30.819 --> 00:12:32.139
Sister,

00:12:32.140 --> 00:12:34.339
we were chosen together to come here.

00:12:34.340 --> 00:12:36.060
We should look out for each other.

00:12:38.740 --> 00:12:40.259
You've been locked in the woodshed,

00:12:40.260 --> 00:12:41.899
barely eating, barely warm.

00:12:41.900 --> 00:12:43.219
I made these pastries myself.

00:12:43.220 --> 00:12:45.420
Here. Have a taste.

00:12:52.137 --> 00:12:53.136
It's delicious.

00:12:53.137 --> 00:12:54.018
Thank you.

00:12:54.419 --> 00:12:55.499
Then eat up, Sister.

00:12:55.500 --> 00:12:56.820
I'll deal with Madam Du.

00:13:19.475 --> 00:13:21.418
Used goods and still priced that high?

00:13:21.419 --> 00:13:22.698
She was the top courtesan.

00:13:22.699 --> 00:13:24.058
Men pay fortunes just to see her.

00:13:24.059 --> 00:13:25.859
Now you're getting a bargain.

00:13:31.500 --> 00:13:33.700
You are indeed a brilliant mind.

00:13:34.020 --> 00:13:34.899
But,

00:13:34.900 --> 00:13:37.259
besides drugging your food,

00:13:37.299 --> 00:13:39.619
I've prepared another "gift" for you.

00:13:39.620 --> 00:13:41.499
(So this is your game,
Su Wanniang.)

00:13:41.500 --> 00:13:43.420
(You really are vicious.)

00:13:44.340 --> 00:13:46.899
This is an aphrodisiac incense
from the Western Regions.

00:13:46.900 --> 00:13:49.660
Do you like the scent, Sister?

00:13:50.225 --> 00:13:51.305
Why?

00:13:51.340 --> 00:13:52.859
Why are you doing this to me?

00:13:53.380 --> 00:13:54.339
I've had enough

00:13:54.340 --> 00:13:56.207
of living in your shadow.

00:13:56.380 --> 00:13:57.379
You were the top courtesan,

00:13:57.380 --> 00:13:58.698
you had all the glory.

00:13:58.699 --> 00:14:00.495
Why do you get all the good fortune?

00:14:00.699 --> 00:14:02.698
You crossed someone you shouldn't have.

00:14:02.699 --> 00:14:04.578
Now they want you dead.

00:14:04.579 --> 00:14:05.619
I'm kind.

00:14:05.620 --> 00:14:07.658
So before you die,

00:14:07.659 --> 00:14:09.920
I arranged one last taste
of earthly pleasure.

00:14:12.939 --> 00:14:14.499
Tonight,

00:14:14.939 --> 00:14:16.099
you shall

00:14:16.179 --> 00:14:17.979
enjoy yourself.

00:14:19.212 --> 00:14:20.252
You...

00:14:22.625 --> 00:14:23.739
What a pity.

00:14:23.740 --> 00:14:25.099
Don't worry, beauty.

00:14:25.779 --> 00:14:27.139
I promise

00:14:27.620 --> 00:14:30.700
you'll die happy.

00:14:32.100 --> 00:14:34.139
(Liu Ruyan's memories
are surfacing again...)

00:14:35.059 --> 00:14:37.139
(He has the same tattoo...)

00:14:37.579 --> 00:14:39.180
(as the men who hunted her.)

00:14:46.939 --> 00:14:48.779
You bit me! Why you little...